data.description: Huge price reduction! Perfect sized home for your desert getaway. This San Vicente floor plan, at 1,574 sq. ft gives you a primary bed and bath on one side and second bed, bath, and den down a separate hallway for lots of privacy from guests. There is a fireplace for cold winter nights and newer stainless-steel appliances in the kitchen for when you want to cook up something for friends. The owner even added a lovely screened in porch for enjoying the nighttime desert air and the lot is situated lower than the neighbor in the back for complete privacy! This property just needs your special touch to make it your next home! Sun City Shadow Hills is a premier destination for 55 plus active adults that want to have two highly rated golf courses, all the amenities you could want and 60+ clubs for you to join and make new friends. Come take a look and imagine all the possibilities!
